data.description: Welcome to this well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo.  Situated in a gated community with meticulously maintained grounds, residents also have access to a community playground. Step inside to discover the vaulted ceilings that graces the spacious living areas with all the natural lighting.  Newly painted. The large master bedroom features an ensuite with a deck , creating a private retreat within your own home.  The kitchen is well-appointed with ample counter space, making it a pleasure to work in, and the condo provides plenty of storage space for your convenience.  The location is unbeatable, offering proximity to golf courses, Valley Fair Mall, and sits right between the major highways (I-15 and I-215), a plethora of dining and shopping options, entertainment venues, and more. Don't miss this incredible opportunity - schedule a showing today and be prepared to fall in love!   The condo is FHA and VA approved. Square footage figures are approximate and should be independently verified by the buyer.
